# 浏览器打开: http://localhost:8080/doc.html

####################################
### 8. 完整业务流程测试
####################################

### 场景: 用户从注册到完成学习的完整流程

### Step 1: 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student001",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "student001@example.com",
  "nickname": "学员001"
}

### Step 2: 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Step 3: 浏览课程列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course/course/list?current=1&size=10

### Step 4: 查看课程详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course/course/1

### Step 5: 查看课程章节
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course/chapter/course/1

### Step 6: 创建订单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "courseIds": [1],
  "remark": "购买Java课程"
}

### Step 7: 快捷支付
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/api/payments/quick-pay
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "orderNo": "替换为实际订单号",
  "paymentMethod": 1,
  "amount": 199.00
}

### Step 8: 开始学习，更新进度
POST http://localhost:8080/api/learning/learning/record/progress
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "lessonId": 1,
  "progress": 300,
  "duration": 600
}

### Step 9: 创建学习笔记
POST http://localhost:8080/api/learning/learning/note
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "lessonId": 1,
  "content": "今天学习了Java基础，收获很多！",
  "timepoint": 300
}

### Step 10: 发表课程评论
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course/comment
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "content": "课程质量很高，值得推荐！",
  "rating": 5
}

### Step 11: 获取学习统计
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learning/learning/record/stats
X-User-Id: 1

### Step 12: 向AI提问
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ai/chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 1

{
  "question": "如何更好地学习Java？",
  "conversationId": "conv-student001"
}

### Step 13: 获取AI课程推荐
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ai/recommend/courses?limit=5
X-User-Id: 1

### Step 14: 生成学习分析报告
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ai/analysis/report
X-User-Id: 1
